<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', 'Cantarell', 'Fira Sans', 'Droid Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fafafa 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            color: #000000;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
        }
        .header {
            padding: 40px 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background: #000000;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 40px 40px;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #444444;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 32px;
            background: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background 0.2s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: #333333;
        }
        .divider {
            margin: 32px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .divider::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 50%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background: #eaeaea;
        }
        .divider span {
            position: relative;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 0 16px;
        }
        .link-box {
            background: #fafafa;
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 16px;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666666;
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background: #fff3f3;
            border: 1px solid #ffc9c9;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }
        .alert-box h3 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #d32f2f;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .alert-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #c62828;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .tips-box {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
        .tips-box h3 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .tips-box ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .tips-box li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #555555;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .tips-box li::before {
            content: '‚Ä¢';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #000000;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 32px 40px;
            background: #fafafa;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .container {
                margin: 20px auto;
                border-radius: 0;
                border-left: none;
                border-right: none;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding-left: 24px;
                padding-right: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üîí</div>
            <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Secure your account with a new password</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="message">
                We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to create a new password for your account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.
            </p>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider">
                <span>OR COPY LINK</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="link-box">{{resetLink}}</div>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Alert</h3>
                <p>
                    If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately. Your current password will remain unchanged until you create a new one.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tips-box">
                <h3>Creating a Strong Password</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use at least 8 characters (longer is better)</li>
                    <li>Mix uppercase and lowercase letters</li>
                    <li>Include numbers and special characters</li>
                    <li>Avoid common words or personal information</li>
                    <li>Don't reuse passwords from other accounts</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>¬© 2025 FD Auth. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
